ess to the Serpent-hunter which has NO STAT REQUIREMENTS, A STR scaling at +10, and at 12 weight probably weighs less than your main weapon+shield in a pure STR character.<br/><br/>TLDR: Stop complaining about Bestial Sling, go get a good shield and a pokey stick. </p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16610920" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16610920" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">7</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>47</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>25</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16610920"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16610920" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16610920"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
